         <xocs:funding-text>This study was supported through a grant of the Stemmler Foundation, a member of the Stifterverband für die Deutsche Wissenschaft, to C. Leuschner. This support is gratefully acknowledged. We are also grateful to the Poloniny National Park authority, the local forest administrations and the Ministry of Defence of the Slovak Republic for the permits to conduct the study and for technical support during the field work. Many thanks also to Peter Hajek for support during sample collection and two anonymous reviewers for helpful comments on an earlier draft.</xocs:funding-text>
