            <ce:table xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/cals/dtd" frame="topbot" id="t0020" rowsep="0" colsep="0">
               <ce:label>Table 4</ce:label>
               <ce:caption id="cn0045">
                  <ce:simple-para id="sp0055" view="all">Results of a PCA analysis based on the six beech forests and data on their soil SOC and N pools, stand structural characteristics and soil chemical properties. Given are the Eigenvalues of the four main axes (fraction of total variation explained) and the loadings of 12 variables on these axes; the values in brackets give the cumulative fraction of variance of the variable explained. The most important factors on each axis are printed in bold.</ce:simple-para>
